searchParallelPlane() - Method in class datacube.search.share.abstracts.AbstractSearch3D
Selects all planes that have points: x = x0 + 1, y = y0 - 1, z = z0 + 1
x = x0 + 1, y = y0 + 1, z = z0 + 1
x = x0 + 1, y = y0 - 1, z = z0 - 1
x = x0 + 1, y = y0 + 1, z = z0 - 1
and starts scheduling task search units for these 2D planes
For these planes, search task units will search the given word only diagonal dimensions to avoid a duplicated search with AbstractSearch3D.searchXY(), AbstractSearch3D.searchXZ() and AbstractSearch3D.searchYZ()
SearchParallelPlane1 - Class in datacube.search.share.impl
This class is an extension of AbstractSearch3D
Invoke all scheduled unit tasks that the given word will be searched in the planes of x = x0 + 1, y = y0 - 1, z = z0 + 1

searchXY() - Method in class datacube.search.share.abstracts.AbstractSearch3D
Selects all planes that are perpendicular to Z dimensions and and starts scheduling task search units for these 2D planes
For these planes, search task units will search the given word through 3 dimensions: horizontal, vertical and diagonal
searchXZ() - Method in class datacube.search.share.abstracts.AbstractSearch3D
Selects all planes that are perpendicular to Y dimensions and and starts scheduling task search units for these 2D planes
For these planes, search task units will search the given word only diagonal dimensions to avoid a duplicated search with AbstractSearch3D.searchXY()
searchYZ() - Method in class datacube.search.share.abstracts.AbstractSearch3D
Selects all planes that are perpendicular to X dimensions and and starts scheduling task search units for these 2D planes
For these planes, search task units will search the given word only diagonal dimensions to avoid a duplicated search with AbstractSearch3D.searchXY()
